Mitzi Kapture https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mitzi_Kapture 0 Mitzi Kapture (born as Mitzi Gaynor Donahue on May 2, 1962) is an American actress, known for her role as Sgt. Rita Lee Lance in the CBS/USA Network crime drama series Silk Stalkings from 1991 to 1995.
